ustomers","[Compliance] Register beneficial owners in national registry","[Compliance] File suspicious activity reports (SAR) within 24 hours","[Compliance] Screen customers against UN and national sanctions lists"],"phase":2},{"epic_id":"EPIC-08F41C3F","title":"Manage Education & Literacy Engagement","subdomain_group":"Manage Regulatory Engagement","description":"Establish a comprehensive education and financial literacy engagement capability that enables the Investment Bank to fulfil regulatory outreach obligations within Digital Financial Regulation Core Operations. This capability supports Regulatory Engagement by delivering structured literacy programmes, stakeholder communications, and compliance-aligned educational content to clients, employees, and regulators.","business_value":"Strengthen regulatory trust and reduce compliance breaches by 25% through proactive client education; enhance market reputation and client retention by delivering measurable financial literacy uplift across high-risk customer segments.","strategic_rationale":"Per Gartner Top Trends 2025 (AI-Powered Digital Transformation), enterprises using AI report 20-30% productivity gains and 15% cost reduction on average — applying Generative AI and agentic workflows to literacy engagement enables scalable, personalised regulatory education with measurable ROI.","governance_reference":"FATF Recommendations (AML/CFT) — FATF","trend_alignment":"AI-Powered Digital Transformation","risk_register":["AI-generated literacy content may misrepresent regulatory obligations if RAG grounding and human review controls are inadequate, exposing the bank to FATF non-compliance findings.","Low client engagement with literacy programmes could undermine evidence of risk-based AML/CFT outreach, weakening regulator confidence and audit outcomes."],"estimated_sprints":6,"features":[{"title":"Regulatory Literacy Content Platform","description":"AI-powered content authoring and delivery platform for regulatory and financial literacy programmes targeting clients and internal staff.","technical_notes":"Leverage Generative AI for content personalisation, Vector databases for semantic search of regulatory materials, and AMD MI300X inference for low-latency multilingual delivery.","user_stories":[{"role":"Regulatory Engagement Manager","want":"to publish AI-generated, jurisdiction-specific literacy content aligned to FATF guidance","so_that":"clients receive accurate, timely education that reduces compliance risk","acceptance_criteria":["Content auto-tagged to FATF Recommendation references","Multilingual delivery supported across 5 jurisdictions","Content review workflow enforces 4-eyes approval"],"tasks":[{"title":"Build GenAI content authoring pipeline","description":"Implement LLM-based authoring service with retrieval over vector store of FATF and national regulatory texts.","estimated_days":8,"assignee_role":"Solutions Architect"},{"title":"Configure 4-eyes approval workflow","description":"Build dual-approval workflow with audit trail aligned to FATF governance expectations.","estimated_days":4,"assignee_role":"Compliance Engineer"}]}],"estimated_story_points":8},{"title":"Stakeholder Engagement & Outreach Orchestration","description":"Agentic workflow capability to orchestrate targeted regulatory outreach campaigns, training nudges, and engagement reporting to regulators.","technical_notes":"Use Agentic workflows to segment audiences, trigger personalised nudges, and generate regulator-facing engagement evidence packs.","user_stories":[{"role":"Compliance Officer","want":"to orchestrate enhanced-due-diligence education journeys for high-risk customers","so_that":"we evidence proactive AML/CFT engagement to FATF-aligned regulators","acceptance_criteria":["High-risk segments identified via sanctions and PEP screening feeds","Outreach completion tracked per customer with audit log","Regulator evidence pack auto-generated quarterly"],"tasks":[{"title":"Integrate sanctions screenin