tment Management","subdomain_group":"Product Specific Fulfillment","description":"This capability enables the retail bank to manage end-to-end investment products and services including account management, portfolio oversight, electronic trading, planning, and analytics. The scope covers Product Specific Fulfillment within Retail Banking Core Operations, ensuring regulatory-compliant investment lifecycle management.","business_value":"Increase investment AUM by 15% through enhanced portfolio management capabilities; Reduce operational risk and regulatory capital charges by aligning with Basel IV standardised approaches.","strategic_rationale":"Open banking generates $416B in revenue opportunity by 2026 (McKinsey Global Banking Annual Review 2024); BNPL captures 5% of global e-commerce payments, driving the need for embedded investment services and API-enabled portfolio access.","governance_reference":"Basel IV (CRR3/CRD6) — BIS / European Parliament","trend_alignment":"Open Banking & Embedded Finance","risk_register":["Regulatory non-compliance with Basel IV output floor and IRRBB requirements leading to capital penalties","Integration complexity with legacy core banking and trading systems extending delivery beyond 12 weeks"],"estimated_sprints":6,"features":[{"title":"Manage Investment Account","description":"Provides onboarding, maintenance, and servicing of client investment accounts with integrated KYC and regulatory controls.","technical_notes":"Leverage PSD2/Open Banking APIs for account aggregation and embedded finance SDKs for partner integration.","user_stories":[{"role":"Investment Operations Officer","want":"to open and maintain investment accounts via a unified digital workflow","so_that":"clients can be onboarded rapidly with full regulatory compliance","acceptance_criteria":["Account opening completes within 5 minutes end-to-end","KYC/AML checks integrated with core banking","Standardised approach for credit risk applied to account exposures"],"tasks":[{"title":"Design account onboarding API","description":"Define REST endpoints aligned with PSD2 Open Banking standards for investment account creation.","estimated_days":5,"assignee_role":"Solutions Architect"},{"title":"Implement KYC integration service","description":"Build integration with KYC provider and core banking to automate identity and risk checks.","estimated_days":7,"assignee_role":"Data Engineer"}]}],"estimated_story_points":8},{"title":"Manage Investment Portfolio Management","description":"Enables active management of client portfolios including rebalancing, allocation, and performance tracking.","technical_notes":"Use AI credit scoring and real-time analytics engines for portfolio risk and allocation decisions.","user_stories":[{"role":"Portfolio Manager","want":"to rebalance portfolios based on target allocations and risk limits","so_that":"client portfolios remain aligned to mandates and regulatory limits","acceptance_criteria":["Rebalance proposals generated daily per portfolio","Output floor of 72.5% of standardised RWA applied to portfolio capital calculations","Audit trail captured for all rebalance actions"],"tasks":[{"title":"Build rebalancing engine","description":"Develop calculation engine for optimal allocation using Basel IV standardised RWA inputs.","estimated_days":8,"assignee_role":"Quant Developer"},{"title":"Integrate RWA output floor calculation","description":"Implement 72.5% output floor logic within portfolio capital assessment module.","estimated_days":6,"assignee_role":"Risk Engineer"}]}],"estimated_story_points":13},{"title":"Manage eTrading Workbench","description":"Provides a unified electronic trading interface for order entry, routing, and execution across asset classes.","technical_notes":"Leverage real-time payment rails and low-latency messaging for order routing and settlement.","user_stories":[{"role":"Trader","want":"to execute trades through a single workbench with real-time market data","so_that":"trades are ex